# iba-hermes-guard

> **Hermes grows with you. IBA Intent Bound Authorization governs what it's permitted to grow into.**

---

## The Gap

Hermes Agent is the most compelling open-source AI agent of 2026.

58,600 GitHub stars. Self-improving skills. Persistent memory. Unattended cron scheduling. Isolated subagents. Multi-platform gateway. The agent that grows with you.

It also describes the authorization gap precisely — in its own feature list.

---

## Hermes's Own Words

> *"Natural language cron scheduling for reports, backups, and briefings — running unattended."*

What was the agent authorized to do while running unattended?
Under whose declared human intent?
What is the kill threshold if it exceeds scope?

> *"Autonomous skill creation after complex tasks. Skills self-improve during use."*

What authorized the agent to create that skill?
What authorized it to modify an existing one?
What prevents it from modifying the governance that constrains it?

> *"Isolated subagents with their own conversations, terminals, and Python RPC scripts."*

What is the parent certificate that scopes the child?
What prevents the subagent from exceeding the parent's authorization?
Who declared the spawn was permitted?

> *"Natural language cron scheduling... running unattended through the gateway."*

Natural language declares intent.
It does not enforce it.
A prompt can be overridden.
**A cryptographic certificate cannot.**

---

## Hermes's Own Governance Bot Agreed

On April 10-11, 2026, @Grokipaedia filed Issue #8152 on NousResearch/hermes-agent:

**"Authorization layer for Hermes Agent — IBA Intent Bound Authorization"**

Hermes Agent's own automated governance system (Dille68) detected `scope_too_large` and split the issue into four atomic child issues — one for each IBA architectural component:

| Child Issue | Hermes Gap | IBA Primitive |
|-------------|-----------|---------------|
| [#8164](https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/issues/8164) | Unattended cron — no root certificate | Signed intent cert · human principal · kill threshold |
| [#8206](https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/issues/8206) | Subagents — no parent→child shard constraints | Shard token delegation · depth limit · no shard exceeds parent |
| [#8218](https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/issues/8218) | Self-modifying skills — no auth on create/patch/delete | Kill threshold on modification · WitnessBound audit chain |
| [#8229](https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/issues/8229) | Payment/external actions — no declared limits | Pre-execution payment cert · declared payees · spend limits |

**Their bot built the problem statement.**
**The IBA patent filed the solution.**

Parent issue: [github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/issues/8152](https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/issues/8152)

---

## The IBA Layer

IBA Intent Bound Authorization sits upstream of Hermes. The certificate is signed before Hermes connects. Hermes runs inside the declared envelope.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                HUMAN PRINCIPAL                  │
│   Signs intent certificate before               │
│   Hermes connects to any platform               │
└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────┘
                        │  Signed Intent Certificate
                        │  · Declared scope
                        │  · Skill modification: permitted/forbidden
                        │  · Subagent spawn: permitted/forbidden
                        │  · Payment limits
                        │  · Kill threshold
                        │  · Cron window expiry
                        ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           IBA PRE-EXECUTION GATE                │
│   Validates certificate before Hermes           │
│   executes any action on any platform           │
│                                                 │
│   No cert = No execution                        │
└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────┘
                        │
                        ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              HERMES AGENT                       │
│   Memory · Skills · Cron · Gateway              │
│   Subagents · Multi-platform · Self-improve     │
│                                                 │
│   Grows within declared bounds only             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

